125
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:43,000
(英文)

126
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:45,000
There is an unexpected twist

127
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,000
between verse 8 and verse 9

128
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:51,000
(英文)

