173
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,000
If you want to over emphasise it

174
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,000
You say it four times

175
00:09:57,000 --> 00:10:08,000
(英文)

176
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:12,000
