Two, we have not been false to your covenant

184
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:36,000
Three, our hearts have not turned back

185
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:38,000
Four, for emphasis

186
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:42,000
Nor have our steps departed from your ways

